%F A357733 a(n) = k(n)*sqrt((k(n)+1)^2/3 + 1)/4 for odd n,
%F A357733 a(n) = (k(n) + 1)*sqrt(k(n)^2/3 + 1)/4 for even n,
%F A357733 where k(n) = A356047(n).
